{"tid":1566613,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"長期背痛，想換床褥，有冇邊隻牌子嘅床褥介紹？","createTime":"2019-09-13T16:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T02:53:24.000Z","uid":84286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9d8df6bcfba218fd16796d68883a911aafff5798","tid":1566613,"uid":84286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"長期背痛，睇完醫生，醫生建議換張軟少少嘅床褥，而家個張太硬，<br />\n試過個啲咩喜居樂，愛皇健，成六七千一張，覺得唔係好啱我<br />\n跟住試過張Sealy,有張Response Premium,試完覺得好正，不過特價都要8千幾<br />\n今日試左Emma,又覺得幾好，五千頭就有交易，性價比好高，係我諗住扑槌之際，又見到有個牌子叫Noa,好似又幾好，都係賣泡膠床褥<br />\n有冇巴打試過，Noa 質素係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79ff84dc231c1611fc5eac9076888f058bbb6f5","tid":1566613,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f1c3f5fce73521fc9a24392524550d6f9a4b274","tid":1566613,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"emmas 澳洲果幾張評價唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2faaf063860d342ec64b6bf4e501caf77736e0a","tid":1566613,"uid":84286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f1c3f5fce73521fc9a24392524550d6f9a4b274","tid":1566613,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"emmas 澳洲果幾張評價唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"emmas同emma係兩個牌子黎<br />\nemmas 澳洲造個幾張我試過，係幾舒服，不過折完張張都仲過萬"},{"pid":"52fce990f665f183a11286f6d738fd24fca7f4c6","tid":1566613,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13